<h5>UnicodeText can fix text encoding problem by converting text files to unicode encoding.  It&rsquo;s intuitive and easy to use.  Most of the text formats supported.</h5>

<h5>When files dropped into app, they already been read as unicode encoding. Double click file item to preview the whole file as unicode. Click save button to save the unicode file to file system to finish the coding conversion.</h5>

